7.2 Filling a rectangle
=======================

While the rectangular mode is active, press тАШiтАЩ to fill the rectangle.
You will be asked to choose a character.  You have those options:

   тАв for a regular character like тАШtтАЩ, just type it.
   тАв тАШSPCтАЩ or тАШDELтАЩ for a shade of grey тАШ" тЦСтЦТтЦУтЦИ"тАЩ among the 5 available
     in UNICODE.  тАШSPCтАЩ to make it darker and darker.  тАШDELтАЩ to make the
     rectangle lighter and lighter.
   тАв тАШC-yтАЩ to chose the first character in the top of the kill ring.

   The above selection is the same as for the flood-fill action (see
*note Flood-fill::).


