7.6 ASCII to UNICODE
====================

The standard base-line тАШUnilineтАЩ (тАШINS s 0тАЩ) or тАШaa2u-rectangleтАЩ (тАШINS s
aтАЩ) conversions may be used to convert ASCII art to UNICODE.  The
original ASCII art may be drawn for instance by the тАШartist-modeтАЩ or the
тАШpicture-modeтАЩ packages.

   To use тАШaa2u-rectangleтАЩ, install the тАШascii-art-to-unicodeтАЩ package
by Thien-Thi Nguyen (RIP), available on ELPA.  тАШUnilineтАЩ does not
requires a dependency on this package, by lazy evaluating any call to
тАШaa2u-rectangleтАЩ.  See
<https://elpa.gnu.org/packages/ascii-art-to-unicode.html>




