11 Hydra or Transient?
**********************

The basic usage of тАШUnilineтАЩ should be easy: just move the point, and
lines are traced.  Change brush to draw thicker lines.

   More complex actions are summoned by the тАШ<insert>тАЩ key, with or
without selection.  This is a single key to remember.  Then a textual
menu is displayed, giving the possible keys continuations and their
meaning.  All that is achieved by the тАШHydraтАЩ or тАШTransientтАЩ libraries,
which are now part of тАШEmacsтАЩ (thanks!).

   The тАШHydraтАЩ and тАШTransientтАЩ libraries offer similar features.  Some
users may prefer one or the other.

   тАШUnilineтАЩ was developed from day one with тАШHydraтАЩ.  тАШTransientтАЩ is a
late addition.

