11.4 The Hydra interface
========================

Put that in your тАШ~/.emacsтАЩ file:

     (use-package uniline-hydra
       :bind ("C-<insert>" . uniline-mode))

   It has been asked by тАШTransientтАЩ-only users to avoid installing the
тАШHydraтАЩ package.  Currently, it is not possible to make dependencies
conditional in тАШMelpaтАЩ.  And removing the тАШHydraтАЩ dependency would hurt
тАШHydraтАЩ users.  Therefore, for the time being, the тАШHydraтАЩ package is
still installed when installing тАШUnilineтАЩ through тАШMelpaтАЩ.


