12.8 Font
=========

Face customization is unrelated to тАШUnilineтАЩ.  However, тАШUnilineтАЩ can
assist in choosing a good font and customizing the тАШdefaultтАЩ face.  See
*note Which fonts?::.

   Type тАШ<insert> fтАЩ to select a font just for the current тАШUnilineтАЩ
session.  Type тАШ*тАЩ to enter the тАШEmacsтАЩ customization of the тАШdefaultтАЩ
face and retain your choice for future sessions.


