14.1 Move the cursor
====================

Move cursor while drawing lines by calling any of the 4 directions
functions:
   тАв тАШuniline-write-upтЖСтАЩ
   тАв тАШuniline-write-riтЖТтАЩ
   тАв тАШuniline-write-dwтЖУтАЩ
   тАв тАШuniline-write-lfтЖРтАЩ

   They expect a repeat тАШcountтАЩ (usually 1) and optionally тАШforce=tтАЩ to
overwrite the buffer


