14.2 Brush
==========

Set the current brush by calling any of the following:

   тАв тАШuniline--set-brush-nilтАЩ ;; write nothing
   тАв тАШuniline--set-brush-0тАЩ ;; eraser
   тАв тАШuniline--set-brush-1тАЩ ;; single thin lineтХ╢тФАтХ┤
   тАв тАШuniline--set-brush-2тАЩ ;; single thick lineтХ║тФБтХ╕
   тАв тАШuniline--set-brush-3тАЩ ;; double lineтХ║тХРтХ╕
   тАв тАШuniline--set-brush-blockтАЩ ;; blocks тЦЩтЦДтЦЯтЦА

   Those functions are equivalent to:

   тАв тАШ(setq uniline--brush nil)тАЩ
   тАв тАШ(setq uniline--brush 0)тАЩ
   тАв тАШ(setq uniline--brush 1)тАЩ
   тАв тАШ(setq uniline--brush 2)тАЩ
   тАв тАШ(setq uniline--brush 3)тАЩ
   тАв тАШ(setq uniline--brush :block)тАЩ

   except the functions also update the mode-line.


